originalText.text: Today, I visited Rose at her new location in the city (Meat Packing District) for another PRP session, and I’m in love with her new location and suite! Rose is always super professional but also very personal and welcoming. I’ve visited larger medical spas in the past but always felt overwhelmed having to see different injectors. With Rose, my treatments are always personalized, and I know what to expect. If you are contemplating getting aesthetic treatments, Trust me; Rose is your girl!
